- What's his name?

01:17.970 --> 01:20.393
- Ryan Witherspoon.
- Witherspoon?

01:20.393 --> 01:21.889
He go to your school?

01:22.271 --> 01:25.771
He's going to post next year, okay?

01:28.343 --> 01:30.963
Okay, I guess he's cute.

01:34.348 --> 01:36.320
On the LIE a multi-vehicle accident

01:36.320 --> 01:39.529
just before the mid-town tunnel
has traffic clogged up...

01:41.474 --> 01:43.198
Is that a tattoo?

01:44.037 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:46.563 --> 01:47.830
Where'd you get it?

01:47.830 --> 01:49.284
Well, you've got tattoos.

01:49.284 --> 01:51.939
I was 18 and in the service.

01:52.124 --> 01:55.543
It's henna. It washes off.

01:56.067 --> 01:57.708
Why didn't you just tell me that?

01:57.708 --> 02:01.347
I just did. You're such a cop.

02:01.347 --> 02:03.745
Yeah, wait till you have kids.

02:04.902 --> 02:07.535
All the little Witherspoons.

02:14.600 --> 02:16.075
Move.

02:19.226 --> 02:22.757
Stay here, lock the doors,
roll up that window.

02:30.889 --> 02:32.994
Stabler, Manhattan SVU, watch yourself.

02:32.994 --> 02:35.382
Hurry up, there's someone under there.

02:38.473 --> 02:39.750
Get it out!

02:40.471 --> 02:43.253
All right, call it in, secure the scene.

02:52.918 --> 02:54.242
Don't look at that.

02:57.410 --> 02:59.049
Don't look at that.

