16:56.702 --> 16:58.434
Locals are surveilling it till we get there.

16:58.434 --> 17:00.029
Great. Find something.

17:05.599 --> 17:07.830
Blood. Pop it.

17:10.349 --> 17:12.180
Nobody home.

17:12.180 --> 17:14.910
