I will stay in jail!

30:22.439 --> 30:28.271
I will, but, please, leave me alone.

30:31.883 --> 30:36.183
It's murder two.
He's returning his own indictment.

30:36.362 --> 30:38.489
Sorry, Captain.

30:55.984 --> 30:57.208
Dad?

30:58.098 --> 30:59.692
