31:05.222 --> 31:07.618
Right, what was I thinking?

31:07.618 --> 31:09.926
- Want something to drink?
- No.

31:12.646 --> 31:14.153
Dad...

31:14.999 --> 31:18.763
what that boy Michael did to that man...

31:19.353 --> 31:23.178
That man was supposed to
take care of Michael

31:23.178 --> 31:27.623
and instead he molested him.

31:27.623 --> 31:32.202
He abused him physically,
he betrayed his trust, and I think Michael...

31:32.202 --> 31:34.945
just had enough.

31:34.945 --> 31:38.874
- So what happens now?
- He's probably gonna go to prison.

31:39.351 --> 31:42.252
All he's gotta do is tell the truth.

31:42.252 --> 31:44.386
What is it with you kids?

31:44.386 --> 31:47.039
It's hard to talk to adults.

31:47.039 --> 31:48.700
Why?

31:48.905 --> 31:50.946
You're always judging us.

31:50.946 --> 31:52.730
You expect us to be like you

31:52.730 --> 31:54.493
and you get mad if we're not.

31:54.493 --> 31:56.618
It's just easier to talk to our friends.

31:56.618 --> 31:58.209
What if you don't have any friends?

31:58.209 --> 32:01.314
- Everybody's got friends.
- Yeah? Well, who do you talk to?

32:01.314 --> 32:03.015
Dad.

32:03.579 --> 32:05.510
You talk to Ryan Witherspoon?

32:05.510 --> 32:08.513
More than you talk to Mom.

32:13.065 --> 32:15.374
Grand Jury Room
Thursday, September 14

32:15.374 --> 32:18.072
Could the wound have been inflicted
during a struggle for the gun?

32:18.072 --> 32:20.316
- Not likely.
- Why not?

32:20.316 --> 32:24.279
The size of the entry wound the force
at which it entered suggests close range.

32:24.279 --> 32:25.550
But there was no stippling.

32:25.550 --> 32:27.165
Stippling is?

32:27.165 --> 32:28.736
When lead leaves the muzzle,

32:28.736 --> 32:31.627
it's followed by the charge that fires it,
the gunpowder.

32:31.627 --> 32:35.670
At close range it leaves a residue,
point blank it embeds in the skin.

32:35.670 --> 32:37.046
That's stippling.

32:37.046 --> 32:38.458
The size and force of the entry

32:38.458 --> 32:41.152
and the lack of stippling lead you
to conclude?

32:41.152 --> 32:44.852
The gun was three to four feet from
the victim's head when it was fired.

32:44.852 --> 32:46.856
The victim's reach was only 32 inches.

32:46.856 --> 32:49.440
He couldn't have held the gun
three feet from his skull,

32:49.440 --> 32:52.517
much less fired it
into the back of his head.

32:52.517 --> 32:54.810
The body was discovered
wrapped in a sheet.

32:54.810 --> 32:59.233
It was blood-soaked from a head wound
and the genital region was on fire.

32:59.233 --> 33:00.454
Where?

33:00.454 --> 33:03.776
In the dunes about 50 yards off
Cross Bay Boulevard

33:03.776 --> 33:08.195
a medical bracelet on the victim indicated
he lived at West 83rd in Manhattan.

33:08.195 --> 33:12.712
Blood splattered the headboard, wall,
and lamp in the master bedroom.

33:12.712 --> 33:15.217
Did the blood pattern indicate
anything to you?

33:15.217 --> 33:18.542
Yes, that the victim had been shot
while lying in the bed.

33:18.542 --> 33:20.296
Any signs of a struggle?

33:20.296 --> 33:22.707
No. / Forced entry?

33:22.707 --> 33:24.107
No.

33:24.726 --> 33:27.055
The victim's car was missing?

33:27.055 --> 33:30.336
State police located it in Millbrook,
New York.

33:30.336 --> 33:33.479
The murder weapon was found
locked in the trunk.

33:33.479 --> 33:35.749
Who had the keys?

33:37.043 --> 33:39.338
Michael Goren.

33:43.619 --> 33:46.744
- How'd it go in there?
- The kid's toast.

33:46.744 --> 33:50.996
I've been thinking about something
Maureen said last night,
something about friends.

33:50.996 --> 33:52.750
What about them?

33:52.750 --> 33:55.155
You up for taking a little ride?

33:55.883 --> 33:57.771
Adams High School
Millbrook Township, NY
Thursday, September 14

33:57.771 --> 34:00.580
Denise, how long were you
seeing Michael?

34:01.879 --> 34:03.935
What should I say?
I really want to help him.

34:03.935 --> 34:07.050
You can help him by telling us the truth.

34:07.235 --> 34:09.280
We were dating about three months.

34:09.280 --> 34:11.639
He ever talk about Andrew?

34:13.025 --> 34:15.043
Denise?

34:15.605 --> 34:17.616
Did he? / Please.

34:18.938 --> 34:21.634
They didn't get along.

34:22.091 --> 34:24.158
My dad would let Michael stay
in our spare bedroom

34:24.158 --> 34:26.145
when Andrew was out of town.

34:26.145 --> 34:28.791
My parents really liked him.

34:30.475 --> 34:35.313
Sometimes Michael lied about Andrew
being gone, so he could stay over.

34:35.500 --> 34:37.529
Did Andrew ever find out?

34:37.529 --> 34:40.297
- I think he knew.
- He object?

34:41.378 --> 34:43.887
Not after that thing with Danny.

34:43.887 --> 34:45.730
Who's Danny?

34:45.730 --> 34:48.114
Danny Burrell. Michael's best friend.

34:48.114 --> 34:50.734
- What happened?
- I don't know.

34:50.938 --> 34:52.637
But it had to be bad.

34:52.637 --> 34:55.061
I mean, one day they're best friends

34:55.061 --> 34:58.350
and the next day,
it's like they hate each other.

34:59.107 --> 35:01.503
Heads up, Mueller!
Heads up!

35:01.503 --> 35:03.177
Danny Burrell!

35:03.436 --> 35:04.527
Yeah?

35:04.527 --> 35:06.672
Front and center.

35:08.279 --> 35:10.983
We're not friends anymore.

35:10.983 --> 35:12.456
Why not?

35:12.456 --> 35:13.809
Guy's weird, that's all.

35:13.809 --> 35:15.738
What do you mean?
Weird, how?

35:15.738 --> 35:17.153
Just weird.

35:17.153 --> 35:19.493
Did Andrew Croft attack you?

35:20.847 --> 35:23.732
- Did Michael tell you that?
- Why don't you tell us about it?

35:24.193 --> 35:26.140
Man, he swore!

35:28.505 --> 35:31.011
I'm sorry I can't talk in front of her.

35:31.011 --> 35:32.508
That's okay.

35:35.816 --> 35:38.088
- Mike and me played ball.
- Okay.

35:38.088 --> 35:41.741
We went to his house
afterwards to clean up.

35:41.741 --> 35:46.211
He said that Andrew was gone,
so I used his shower, and when I got out...

35:46.211 --> 35:48.554
- he was standing there.
- Andrew?

35:48.808 --> 35:50.188
Yeah.

35:50.472 --> 35:52.466
He was naked.

35:53.246 --> 35:57.062
He was touching himself.

35:57.062 --> 35:59.917
He wanted to dry me off.

35:59.917 --> 36:01.876
He's just a creep.

36:02.158 --> 36:06.668
Anyway, he said that Michael was
too swarthy but I was perfect for him.

36:06.668 --> 36:11.077
He grabbed me, I fought him off,
I screamed for Mike...

36:11.077 --> 36:14.088
and I finally got the door open,
and Michael was...

36:14.088 --> 36:16.214
He was just standing there.

36:16.214 --> 36:19.383
So, I just grabbed my clothes and I ran.

36:19.383 --> 36:21.755
I forgot my Nikes.

36:22.128 --> 36:23.803
You and Michael talk after that?

36:23.803 --> 36:27.697
No way. I told the guy to leave me alone.

36:27.697 --> 36:29.523
I think it's disgusting what he
and Andrew were doing.

36:29.523 --> 36:31.557
You think Michael liked it?

36:32.513 --> 36:33.531
What do you think?

36:33.531 --> 36:36.859
I mean, Michael's 6 foot,
guy benches, what, 220 pounds?

36:36.859 --> 36:39.441
He could kick his ass
if he didn't like him doing him.

36:39.441 --> 36:43.134
He was eight years old
when Andrew started doing him.

36:43.134 --> 36:45.438
Eight-year-olds can't fight back.

36:45.438 --> 36:47.079
Now you tell me where
a 16 year-old's gonna turn

36:47.079 --> 36:50.033
when his best friend turns on him?

36:55.480 --> 36:58.223
Grand Jury Room
Monday, September 18

36:58.223 --> 37:00.767
You said the gun went off
in the midst of a struggle?

37:00.767 --> 37:01.840
Yes.

37:01.840 --> 37:05.780
The police found no signs of a struggle.
How do you explain that?

37:06.035 --> 37:07.438
I don't know.

37:07.438 --> 37:10.285
That's because there was no struggle,
was there?

37:10.285 --> 37:11.673
We struggled.

37:11.673 --> 37:12.629
Over the gun?

37:12.629 --> 37:14.202
Yes. / And it went off?

37:14.202 --> 37:16.121
Yes. / In both your hands?

37:16.121 --> 37:17.468
Yes.

37:17.682 --> 37:21.224
The Coroner found no trace of gunpowder
on the deceased's hands.

37:21.224 --> 37:23.884
I told you what happened.

37:25.530 --> 37:27.902
Who is Danny Burrell?

37:33.489 --> 37:35.351
He's my friend.

37:35.351 --> 37:39.245
Did you witness the deceased
sexually assault Danny Burrell?

37:39.245 --> 37:40.960
No!

37:42.755 --> 37:48.030
Danny will testify the deceased sexually
assaulted him and that you witnessed it.

37:48.030 --> 37:51.047
Are you saying he's lying?

37:53.269 --> 37:58.716
Did Andrew Croft sexually assault
Danny Burrell?

38:02.271 --> 38:04.301
Yes.

38:05.222 --> 38:08.086
And you, too?

38:17.069 --> 38:20.279
Since I was eight.

38:20.732 --> 38:23.459
You shot him to stop him
from molesting you?

38:23.459 --> 38:24.989
No!

38:26.258 --> 38:30.708
I hated it, but I was used to it.

38:30.708 --> 38:35.320
I shot him because he was
bringing over his friend.

38:35.779 --> 38:38.208
What friend?

38:40.809 --> 38:46.465
In Millbrook,
this guy came up sometimes.

38:47.369 --> 38:50.174
Andrew made me do things with him.

38:50.174 --> 38:53.091
When we moved here,
I thought it was over.

38:53.091 --> 38:56.252
But then I come home from school
and he's there!

38:56.252 --> 39:00.535
I mean we moved right
across the street from him!

39:02.530 --> 39:06.995
Andrew was bad enough,
but both of them...

39:06.995 --> 39:09.560
I begged him.

39:16.845 --> 39:20.033
Who is this man?

39:24.420 --> 39:25.670
He'll kill me.

39:25.670 --> 39:27.708
He can't hurt you.

39:27.906 --> 39:30.444
You don't know his powers.

39:30.444 --> 39:32.556
Michael, you're in the custody of the
City of New York.

39:32.556 --> 39:34.328
He can't get to you.

39:34.328 --> 39:37.037
He can get to anybody.

39:37.529 --> 39:40.310
And he will to protect his secret.

39:40.310 --> 39:43.946
A child molester only has power
as long as his secret is kept.

39:43.946 --> 39:46.350
You tell the truth, his power is gone.

39:46.350 --> 39:48.253
What's his name, Michael?

39:48.253 --> 39:51.396
I heard them talk about it.
Nobody did anything.

39:51.396 --> 39:55.467
Talk about what?
Who, Michael?

39:59.027 --> 40:01.564
Andrew and...

40:03.714 --> 40:06.680
and Craig Prince.

40:06.877 --> 40:12.175
They killed that boy in Belgium
and nobody did anything!

40:12.175 --> 40:14.439
When did this happen?
What boy?

40:14.439 --> 40:18.222
I was eight.
It was in the papers there.

40:18.222 --> 40:20.882
Nobody did anything.

40:20.882 --> 40:26.164
Craig Prince can get away with anything.

40:28.632 --> 40:31.637
You're gonna protect me?

40:33.796 --> 40:37.862
Write-offs in the third quarter adjusted
by the...

40:37.862 --> 40:39.251
Craig, good news!

40:39.251 --> 40:41.724
Excuse me, this is a classified briefing.

40:41.724 --> 40:44.445
Yeah, Croft's ward, Michael.

40:44.445 --> 40:47.802
The grand jury voted man two.
DA's willing to cut him a deal.

40:47.802 --> 40:48.877
I don't see what that has to do...

40:48.877 --> 40:52.172
Even better news, you're under arrest
for sexual abuse, sodomy,

40:52.172 --> 40:54.519
assault and endangering
the welfare of a child.

40:54.519 --> 40:57.163
- You're hurting me!
- Not our concern.

40:57.163 --> 40:59.598
Craig Prince, you have the right
to remain silent.

40:59.598 --> 41:04.226
If you give up that right, anything you do
or say can and will be used against you.

41:04.226 --> 41:06.248
Capt. Cragen?

41:25.846 --> 41:32.399
This little boy's mother stuck his hands
on a frying pan until his fingers burned off.

41:35.053 --> 41:37.366
This rape victim...

41:37.366 --> 41:40.605
required 12 hours of surgery to
have a steel plate into her head

41:40.605 --> 41:45.397
after her attacker pummeled her
with a claw hammer.

41:49.827 --> 41:52.560
This one didn't make it.

41:57.556 --> 41:59.146
Is there anybody on this panel

41:59.146 --> 42:03.632
who doesn't share Det. Stabler's anger
for the perpetrators?

42:03.632 --> 42:05.890
This man is a good cop.

42:07.162 --> 42:10.194
As his commanding officer,
I stand with him

42:10.194 --> 42:13.733
and every good cop who faces
these horrors day after day

42:13.733 --> 42:17.759
and has the strength to keep
their impulses in check.

42:17.759 --> 42:21.903
Now if you can look at these pictures
and not understand that

42:21.903 --> 42:27.854
the problem here isn't Elliot Stabler, is it?

42:34.745 --> 42:37.233
Yeah, that's done.
That's done. / Hello?

42:37.233 --> 42:40.236
- All right, yeah, go get the kids dinner...
- Yeah.

42:40.236 --> 42:42.082
Kathleen! / Sure.

42:42.082 --> 42:46.175
- Dickie, Elizabeth, dinner's ready!
- All right tomorrow. Captain...

42:46.175 --> 42:49.397
thanks for the support.

42:53.822 --> 42:55.875
Well?

42:59.161 --> 43:01.634
The Morris Commission cleared me.

